## Services

### Brand Identity & Strategy
Full URL: https://duo-studio.co/services/branding-identity-system/

We create brand strategy, logo design, visual identity systems, messaging frameworks, and brand guidelines for established businesses ready to elevate their presence. Typical projects: 8-12 weeks.

Includes: Brand consulting, user personas, competitive analysis, brand messaging, positioning, art direction, logo design, design systems, brand naming, brand guidelines, collateral design.

### Web Design & Development
Full URL: https://duo-studio.co/services/web-design-development/

We design and develop custom-coded websites that match the credibility your business has earned. No templates, no page builders. Typical projects: 10-16 weeks.

Includes: Sitemaps, wireframes, UI/UX design, copywriting, front-end development, back-end development, CMS implementation, SEO optimization, analytics, API integrations.

### Content & Graphic Design
Full URL: https://duo-studio.co/services/graphic-design/

We create marketing collateral, motion graphics, illustrations, and campaign materials that reinforce your brand's credibility across every touchpoint.

Includes: Brand collateral, photography direction, packaging, print design, motion graphics, illustration, content strategy, marketing design, campaign design.

